name: Ash Grey Tweed Bamboo Artists Brush and Pencil Holder Case
description:
Woollen Tweed Fabric and Chocolate Coloured Bamboo Artists Brush and Pencil Holder Case

A fun brush or pencil holder case made from thick ash grey woollen tweed and finished with a tweed button detail. The use of bamboo makes it a light and versatile holder to carry around!

Different sizes have been sewn in to accomodate the different sized brushes/pencils or whatever objects you find useful. The case rolls up when you are finished so it is easy to carry around. 

The fabric has been upcycled from offcuts and clothes to create a unique ethical product. Finished off with a vibrant deep blue ribbon and red heart charm to bind the holder together.

Feel free to check out my colourful and vibrant items.

name: Dandelion Print Card
description:
A beautiful dandelion card made with felt white card and comes with a felt white envelope. Packaged in a biodegradable sleeve. All materials are sustainable and eco-friendly; each print is etched and pressed individually so that each card is unique.

Left blank inside for your own message.
Card size: 114mm x 160mm
